description: Another fisherman from the same trawler, who died in hospital, is named locally.
title: Hook Head: Search for missing fisherman called off for night
title_page: Hook Head: Search for missing fisherman called off for night - BBC News
maintext: RNLI crews and the coastguard are involved in the search for the missing man who was on board the Alize trawler when it sank off the coast of Hook Head.
